    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a salaryman who gets caught in various everyday troubles and overcomes them with <strong>acrobatic bows</strong>. From boss reprimands to client complaints and family issues, showcase your elegant apology skills across different scenarios. What <i>shocking ending</i> awaits?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[]<strong>Unique Bowing Actions</strong>: Master various techniques like spinning and jumping bows to win over others.<br>[]<strong>Diverse Stages</strong>: Experience immersive gameplay in realistic environments like the office, client sites, home, and public spaces.<br>[]<strong>Comical Storyline</strong>: Enjoy a humor-filled scenario that lets you progress while laughing.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recommended For</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[]Those who want to laugh off everyday stress.<br>[]Players seeking a new kind of action game.<br><br>Master the art of apology in “<u>Super Dogeza</u>!”</p></li></ul>",
